âœ¨ Overview
The Generate Notes feature allows users to turn any document content (text, notes, or textbook excerpts) into structured, AI-generated study notes.
Users can select different note styles and specify focus areas. The feature also includes error handling, copy/download options, and fallback notes if the AI fails.
